---
name: v21-native-exact-decimal
---

```scalascript
val rounded = Decimal("12.345").setScale(2, RoundingMode.HALF_UP)
val tenPow = BigInt(10).pow(3)
val fromUnits = Decimal(tenPow, 2)
val sum = rounded + Decimal("0.65")
val product = Decimal("1.20") * Decimal("3")

println(rounded.toPlainString())
println(fromUnits.toPlainString())
println(sum.toPlainString())
println(product.toPlainString())
println(rounded > Decimal("12.34"))
println(fromUnits.toBigInt())
println("due: " + rounded)
```
